---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
  <title>Topsoil Delivery & Lawn Grading in NJ | Ready for Planting</title>
  <!-- Preconexión para recursos externos (mejora rendimiento) -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com">
  <meta name="description" content="Enrich your garden or yard with nutrient-rich topsoil, delivered and spread on site. Get a free estimate today." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://macpavingandsealcoating.com/services/landscaping/top-soil" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="topsoil delivery NJ, nutrient-rich top soil Essex, lawn grading Passaic, garden soil Wallington, landscaping soil NJ, planting-ready topsoil, Essex yard soil" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {

  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Topsoil Delivery in Essex & Passaic | Ready for Planting",
  "url": "https://macpavingandsealcoating.com/services/landscaping/top-soil",
  "description": "Order rich, screened topsoil for your garden or lawn in Wallington, Essex, and Passaic. Delivered and ready for planting. Perfect for sod, flower beds, and more."

  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <Navbar />
  <Breadcrumb items={[{text: "Topsoil Delivery and Lawn Grading in North Jersey", href: "/ Services / Landscaping / Top Soil"}]} />
  <main>
    <Section title="Level, Nutrient-Rich Ground for a Healthier Lawn">
      <p>Topsoil and grading provide the right base for sod, seed, or planting. MAC Paving delivers nutrient-rich soil and expert lawn leveling for North Jersey homeowners.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/landscaping/top_soil_1.webp" alt="Topsoil Delivery & Lawn Grading in NJ | Ready for Planting - Main Image - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="A Strong Start for Every Outdoor Project">
      <p>Proper soil and grading prevent water issues, erosion, and growth failure. Our topsoil is screened and shaped for ideal drainage and planting success.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/landscaping/top_soil_2.webp" alt="Topsoil Delivery & Lawn Grading in NJ | Ready for Planting - Side View - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="Our Grading and Topsoil Installation Process">
      <p>We clear the site, regrade slopes, and spread topsoil evenly for a smooth planting surface. It’s ready for sod, seed, or garden use immediately.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/landscaping/top_soil_3.webp" alt="Topsoil Delivery & Lawn Grading in NJ | Ready for Planting - Close-Up - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
    <Section title="When to Order Topsoil—and What It Can Improve">
      <p>If your lawn is bumpy, bare, or won’t grow, topsoil might be the fix. Great for pre-sod, replanting, or restoring lawn health. Get a free quote today.</p>
      <img src="assets/imgs/service/landscaping/top_soil_4.webp" alt="Topsoil Delivery & Lawn Grading in NJ | Ready for Planting - Work in Progress - MAC Paving and Sealcoating" />
    </Section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <Scripts />
</body>
</html>